{"tid":1024999,"cid":17,"subCid":0,"title":"［多字少圖遊記］我·她·柬埔寨","createTime":"2019-02-17T04:21:38.000Z","updateTime":"2019-03-06T19:28:33.000Z","uid":237361,"like":3,"dislike":36,"uniUserReply":21,"replies":[{"pid":"744c95ca0128a56ddf5bef3ca4184b801aa027db","tid":1024999,"uid":237361,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-17T04:21:38.000Z","msg":"今年冬天，頸巾大衣一直留在衣櫃裏，不見天日。<br />\n整季最冷的數天，我則偏偏飛往柬埔寨。<br />\n我一直想看看那吳哥窟是什麼模樣。<br />\n怕熱的她笑說，<br />\n她可是為我放棄了最喜歡的氣候。<br />\n飛機著陸，從冷藏櫃般的機艙走出，<br />\n撲面而來的是熱浪、陽光和蟲子。"},{"pid":"3e517dc6da378fd7d465eb566114ccf62b21f09c","tid":1024999,"uid":237361,"like":0,"dislike":14,"score":-14,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-17T04:31:51.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/JmnmQTm.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FJmnmQTm.png&h=9ad707c3&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n走下飛機，不足五分鐘的路程，我就已經站在入境職員面前。<br />\n再過了五分鐘，我就已經在機場外找我的司機。<br />\n沒有穿梭巴士，<br />\n沒有電梯，<br />\n沒有幾層樓高的大堂，<br />\n沒有琳琅滿目的餐廳和店鋪。<br />\n我走下飛機，向前走，不知怎地就離開機場了。"},{"pid":"707713888061301b940c8dfdd2127cdd29a56a97","tid":1024999,"uid":237361,"like":0,"dislike":8,"score":-8,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-17T04:37:01.000Z","msg":"Airbnb房東安排了接送的車，<br />\n卻沒給我司機的聯絡方法，只傳來他的一張大頭照。<br />\n我看著機場外數十個東南亞臉孔的中年男人，<br />\n再看一眼手機上的照片，不禁納悶。"},{"pid":"a6f775fe4cda57bcfb7a0ca2edb98beb24e91d58","tid":1024999,"uid":62996,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-17T04:52:44.000Z","msg":"留名<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7818d977d8a97c2bd506f22b53ef917e99dd460a","tid":1024999,"uid":22073,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-17T04:54:57.000Z","msg":"Ok"},{"pid":"1d4a017c02d9cddab4f15e560467622bfcc1ec12","tid":1024999,"uid":237361,"like":0,"dislike":4,"score":-4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-17T05:08:20.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/vQA34pR.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FvQA34pR.png&h=7264696f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n司機最終來了，穿著T裇布褲拖鞋。<br />\n我一邊看著身旁一家四口的美國人走向一部白色房車，<br />\n一邊拉著朋友坐上了司機的tuk tuk車。<br />\n我們四人相對而坐，體會到什麼是風塵僕僕。<br />\n不知是為了躲避迎面而來的沙塵，<br />\n或是什麼別的，<br />\n坐在我旁邊的她挪一挪身體，靠得更近。"},{"pid":"a904aec515c9070a7df52d30eee0530ceb2659af","tid":1024999,"uid":237361,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-17T12:33:09.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/2yvr4Fn.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F2yvr4Fn.png&h=3b326fd3&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n沿路一片荒野，有古道，有西風，有瘦馬，<br />\n還有瘦牛瘦豬瘦羊瘦雞瘦狗瘦小孩，<br />\n彷彿柬國的一切都是瘦骨嶙峋。<br />\n司機對我們說，<br />\n這裏不單是荒野，更是廢土，整個國度的土壤都不適合耕種。<br />\n當我在幾天後回想這一刻，才突然明白為何柬埔寨的食物如此乏味。"},{"pid":"8ebf46a8a0c4cdae1dd82242178d2273b5888526","tid":1024999,"uid":75525,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-17T13:48:50.000Z","msg":"LM<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/smile2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ebc4f52c07e4d044e3357ec54b5c05ee3c0771d6","tid":1024999,"uid":237361,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-17T15:26:57.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/8dwF944.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F8dwF944.png&h=f67588f0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n到達Airbnb，我們整頓行裝，在泳池游了一陣水。<br />\n天色漸暗，便走到暹粒舊市集逛逛。<br />\n夜市中四處都是小孩，他們胸前掛著一個比身體還要大的盤，放滿香口膠香煙火機，以及炸蛇炸蠍子炸蟑螂炸蟲，口中嚷著two dollars two dollars。<br />\n其中一個小女孩似乎還嫌這樣不夠吸引，<br />\n手上把玩著一隻活蜘蛛，放任它在掌心與胸口遊走。<br />\n我走近一看，還有一張紙，photo one dollar。"},{"pid":"d9b0c03f19a47142050c97518cfdac69841419ee","tid":1024999,"uid":46042,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-18T04:00:32.000Z","msg":"巴打讀開文學？"},{"pid":"006d17b67edd8ed6aa503b92905ee09a0c7ce8fb","tid":1024999,"uid":237361,"like":0,"dislike":5,"score":-5,"quote":{"pid":"d9b0c03f19a47142050c97518cfdac69841419ee","tid":1024999,"uid":46042,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-18T04:00:32.000Z","msg":"巴打讀開文學？"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-18T04:10:12.000Z","msg":"平時有睇下"},{"pid":"9a4ea9fd7450331efe7472c77cd7e82b26b1fef4","tid":1024999,"uid":237361,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-18T04:14:22.000Z","msg":"清晨四點，她已經梳洗好，爬到我床上叫醒我。<br />\n我半睡半醒地走到浴室刷牙，回來卻發現她在我床上睡著了。<br />\n包車四點三十分準時在大屋門口等候，岀發往吳哥窟看日出。<br />\n途中經過街邊小檔，買了一個法包作早餐，<br />\n有點像越南的法包，長條麵包烘得鬆脆，夾住一些菜和肉。<br />\n雖然柬埔寨曾是法國的殖民地，但這已是這趟旅程中最法國的東西了。<br />\n啊，價錢也很法國，五美金一個。"},{"pid":"9b8f08f0b16166dd729769591572a303d9ff1e5e","tid":1024999,"uid":35746,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-18T07:45:34.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5fd15707e2bb3a49a5d74cfe59dd158fa3a44975","tid":1024999,"uid":65904,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"quote":{"pid":"9a4ea9fd7450331efe7472c77cd7e82b26b1fef4","tid":1024999,"uid":237361,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-18T04:14:22.000Z","msg":"清晨四點，她已經梳洗好，爬到我床上叫醒我。<br />\n我半睡半醒地走到浴室刷牙，回來卻發現她在我床上睡著了。<br />\n包車四點三十分準時在大屋門口等候，岀發往吳哥窟看日出。<br />\n途中經過街邊小檔，買了一個法包作早餐，<br />\n有點像越南的法包，長條麵包烘得鬆脆，夾住一些菜和肉。<br />\n雖然柬埔寨曾是法國的殖民地，但這已是這趟旅程中最法國的東西了。<br />\n啊，價錢也很法國，五美金一個。"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-18T08:43:29.000Z","msg":"$5USD???<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n啱啱去完返嚟<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/wPu1fQC.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FwPu1fQC.png&h=e5c41406&s={SIZE}\" />呢個半份$0.50USD"},{"pid":"02a95525f616017d11a9cc45c9ca3c933a8d339e","tid":1024999,"uid":237361,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"5fd15707e2bb3a49a5d74cfe59dd158fa3a44975","tid":1024999,"uid":65904,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"quote":{"pid":"9a4ea9fd7450331efe7472c77cd7e82b26b1fef4","tid":1024999,"uid":237361,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-18T04:14:22.000Z","msg":"清晨四點，她已經梳洗好，爬到我床上叫醒我。<br />\n我半睡半醒地走到浴室刷牙，回來卻發現她在我床上睡著了。<br />\n包車四點三十分準時在大屋門口等候，岀發往吳哥窟看日出。<br />\n途中經過街邊小檔，買了一個法包作早餐，<br />\n有點像越南的法包，長條麵包烘得鬆脆，夾住一些菜和肉。<br />\n雖然柬埔寨曾是法國的殖民地，但這已是這趟旅程中最法國的東西了。<br />\n啊，價錢也很法國，五美金一個。"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-18T08:43:29.000Z","msg":"$5USD???<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n啱啱去完返嚟<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/wPu1fQC.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FwPu1fQC.png&h=e5c41406&s={SIZE}\" />呢個半份$0.50USD"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-18T09:57:44.000Z","msg":"嗰時凌晨四點幾 幾條街得一檔開 焗住俾佢劏<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"624ce7c7d2cbd57e160b8abe2cad4742a4e84bad","tid":1024999,"uid":237361,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-18T12:59:39.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/4Sf4e2D.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F4Sf4e2D.png&h=eb1b36d7&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n在售票處買了三日遊的門票，再經過十數分鐘的車程，我們終於到達吳哥窟。<br />\n吳哥窟佔地龐大，主要可分為三個區域：小圈、大圈和外圈，遊客一般亦會依此分開三條路線遊覽。<br />\n著名看日岀的位置就在小圈內，亦可說是柬埔寨的核心。<br />\n從西門進入，不用看地圖，順着人流走，必定會走到小吳哥城的蓮花池。<br />\n五點左右，這裏已經人頭湧湧。<br />\n人潮形成五六排，每個人都佔好位置等日出。"},{"pid":"2642b041991cbad60f878f0fa79a36dfe0fa6d4f","tid":1024999,"uid":237361,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-18T13:06:24.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/n2Cm1KL.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fn2Cm1KL.png&h=7139234a&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/WiDaaC6.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FWiDaaC6.png&h=db24c22c&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Jgt9rbs.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FJgt9rbs.png&h=1eb0e84c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n朱莉亞和彼得四處奔波，想找好位置拍照，不消一會，已不見蹤影。<br />\n只餘下我和她，與眼前的畫。<br />\n夜幕下的小吳哥城只能望見模糊的輪廓。<br />\n夜空漸漸亮起來，面前的宮殿和寺塔亦隨著天色變換顏色，紅橙黃各色的晨曦隱現，<br />\n最後歸於一片晴藍。<br />\n以這幅畫作背景，我和她拍了一張合照，誰料這會是最後一張。"},{"pid":"0b17ac9105a0220f52921bd2029fc94b02e39fc4","tid":1024999,"uid":35746,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-18T13:06:46.000Z","msg":"真心多人到喊，第時都唔知點算"},{"pid":"accf730d50a9b3e7a21f2832aa03be2f2a49a3af","tid":1024999,"uid":9763,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-18T13:54:14.000Z","msg":"4月頭想去<br />\n其實主要係咪都係3日吳哥fuck<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"40882d8814abb27f1c271f42f6c0e192f66a8c72","tid":1024999,"uid":237361,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"accf730d50a9b3e7a21f2832aa03be2f2a49a3af","tid":1024999,"uid":9763,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-18T13:54:14.000Z","msg":"4月頭想去<br />\n其實主要係咪都係3日吳哥fuck<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-18T14:17:32.000Z","msg":"我去咗五日 睇落去會有其他行程"},{"pid":"b4d3fa408db9d7e509fac11e01c98ba0a8e8694c","tid":1024999,"uid":67195,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-18T14:46:33.000Z","msg":"加甜"},{"pid":"6a1199c6f51c838526f8ce4f9d08d6598aa4405c","tid":1024999,"uid":237361,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"0b17ac9105a0220f52921bd2029fc94b02e39fc4","tid":1024999,"uid":35746,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-18T13:06:46.000Z","msg":"真心多人到喊，第時都唔知點算"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-18T15:38:29.000Z","msg":"最估唔到係有咁多大媽去<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2807f725517216b3e692c9a1dd2616d36a6eca35","tid":1024999,"uid":36175,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-18T15:45:33.000Z","msg":"4 月尾想去，睇下仲有咩玩先"},{"pid":"8afa845b3ecb75bedbc6ad3e07b8e68231651a9d","tid":1024999,"uid":35746,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"6a1199c6f51c838526f8ce4f9d08d6598aa4405c","tid":1024999,"uid":237361,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"0b17ac9105a0220f52921bd2029fc94b02e39fc4","tid":1024999,"uid":35746,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-18T13:06:46.000Z","msg":"真心多人到喊，第時都唔知點算"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-18T15:38:29.000Z","msg":"最估唔到係有咁多大媽去<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-18T21:30:38.000Z","msg":"勁多韓國人，強國人<br />\n<br />\n香港人都係偏少"},{"pid":"980b0bf5e067c0fe5b52cadb814d8fa5ade30a4c","tid":1024999,"uid":214997,"like":3,"dislike":2,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-18T23:37:22.000Z","msg":"口語變書面語=有文筆<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/pig2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"439ed9c5780e83bf0c127caa501f060bce75b1e5","tid":1024999,"uid":237361,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-19T00:34:48.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/wbq4iUo.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fwbq4iUo.png&h=f28ea6c7&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/WVheF6d.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FWVheF6d.png&h=56797545&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/V2O5NMe.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FV2O5NMe.png&h=bca0d6ca&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/VesRJjA.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FVesRJjA.png&h=32d23c61&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/wEcKiSW.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FwEcKiSW.png&h=94480f7e&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/VwiEScZ.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FVwiEScZ.png&h=d1a2ca21&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/PqiNgEF.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FPqiNgEF.png&h=11432401&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n據傳吳哥窟在十四世紀建成，原為政治需求與宗教崇拜結合的產物，後來國度覆亡，高棉人遷都金邊，以致吳哥窟一度被世所遺。<br />\n在這裡，歷史的重量與大自然和諧共融。<br />\n當你定睛欣賞石壁上印度教戰神帝䆁天騎住大象征戰四方，身後忽然傳來沉重的腳步聲，你回頭一看，就見遊人騎著大象遊覽，旁邊還有幾隻猴子上竄下跳。"},{"pid":"4c320f90e5e54b7b45c68a2793e4f5fee1042944","tid":1024999,"uid":5759,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-19T06:52:41.000Z","msg":"柬埔寨<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n出快d得唔得？甜呢？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2113ea83c0c29a986b2eeef08e3ac3c06e9a3c5d","tid":1024999,"uid":52252,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"a904aec515c9070a7df52d30eee0530ceb2659af","tid":1024999,"uid":237361,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-17T12:33:09.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/2yvr4Fn.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F2yvr4Fn.png&h=3b326fd3&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n沿路一片荒野，有古道，有西風，有瘦馬，<br />\n還有瘦牛瘦豬瘦羊瘦雞瘦狗瘦小孩，<br />\n彷彿柬國的一切都是瘦骨嶙峋。<br />\n司機對我們說，<br />\n這裏不單是荒野，更是廢土，整個國度的土壤都不適合耕種。<br />\n當我在幾天後回想這一刻，才突然明白為何柬埔寨的食物如此乏味。"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-19T08:10:29.000Z","msg":"有瘦馬<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fa874c4e48cebfe8e1b3ef4f83e13538c76beaad","tid":1024999,"uid":237361,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-19T10:56:32.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/gLitO0S.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FgLitO0S.png&h=872dae4d&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/kjqG80T.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FkjqG80T.png&h=1b8f8aaf&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/S4zEbee.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FS4zEbee.png&h=8606b778&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/CXqDrNA.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FCXqDrNA.png&h=9ed76245&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Q5d9ysB.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FQ5d9ysB.png&h=58c87e2d&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/v6xRMNC.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fv6xRMNC.png&h=458074a3&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/JFw3CUi.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FJFw3CUi.png&h=c57399b6&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/SS0cwej.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FSS0cwej.png&h=595c297b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n參天大樹矗立在古庭院中央，老樹根盤據在門框在窗口在屋簷，讓人分不清橫卧的毗濕奴身下是千頭巨蛇或是樹幹，梵天座下孔雀是開屏了，或只是樹葉的投影。<br />\n印度教諸神在幾百年前的雕刻上栩栩如生，隨處可見；詳和的四面佛像，令你不論走到那裡，都能感受到衪在對你微笑。<br />\n不似她，<br />\n總是若隱若現，若即若離。<br />\n<em>從眉梢中感覺到，從眼角看不到，彷彿已是最直接的裸露。是無力但有心，暗來明往，誰說這算是情愫。</em>"},{"pid":"8cd42b3c0f94842854c05a4795d585cf9bca26f2","tid":1024999,"uid":237361,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-19T12:24:28.000Z","msg":"推下先<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4e3b5adaf7da1d6d329c55b56ab2e545be5b11fc","tid":1024999,"uid":237361,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-19T15:43:02.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3f0d5d2dffbb7519fefb55dc5cfbbc9f74289c6a","tid":1024999,"uid":237361,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-19T15:43:21.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2fdfc3e18e476cc66759f4e760c54a7d07d62706","tid":1024999,"uid":237361,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-19T15:54:18.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/aGCuz66.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FaGCuz66.png&h=ce652828&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/mZBvjyN.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FmZBvjyN.png&h=4ccc92d4&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/uJthJ0t.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FuJthJ0t.png&h=83d59344&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n吳哥窟很大很空曠，陽光猛烈，加上暹粒三十多度的高溫，怕熱的她很快就開始吃不消。<br />\n我和彼得為大家買來冰凍飲料，四大杯果汁只需四十多元港幣。<br />\n她說她的牛油果汁味道很好，遞給我喝了一口。<br />\n一個小女孩走過來兜售雪條。<br />\n她雙眼下意識地就亮起來，我笑著拉住她，示意她看清楚。<br />\n小女孩手上的雪條沒有包裝紙，赤裸裸地暴曬在陽光下，卻絲毫沒有溶化。<br />\n我可不敢吃。<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"300cedfc21ff43d9a2dc5ec63dc099371151478e","tid":1024999,"uid":237361,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-20T13:31:56.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/WXZg6KO.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FWXZg6KO.png&h=5f58b7b5&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/uJcRVC9.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FuJcRVC9.png&h=77b4cde5&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/SkRbVDa.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FSkRbVDa.png&h=69bed836&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n日岀後，自然就是日落。<br />\n我們坐包車從吳哥窟到洞里薩湖看日落，途中大家都累了，昏昏欲睡。<br />\n迷迷糊糊之間，她靠在我的肩上沉沉睡去。<br />\n包車最後停在一個不可稱為碼頭的碼頭，我們轉乘長艇，穿過空邦魯浮村的一排排水上小屋，當地小孩在旁追逐戲水。<br />\n夕陽下的浮村看起來很像大澳的棚屋，大抵日光之下真的無新事。"},{"pid":"874d80a93844c5cc49a7baafe10ad3cc246db1cf","tid":1024999,"uid":193342,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-20T13:37:23.000Z","msg":"留名<br />\n<br />\n幾好睇"},{"pid":"94ec44b4b79ecaaed048bf95d3e6d5fb19355e8c","tid":1024999,"uid":237361,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"874d80a93844c5cc49a7baafe10ad3cc246db1cf","tid":1024999,"uid":193342,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-20T13:37:23.000Z","msg":"留名<br />\n<br />\n幾好睇"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-20T13:43:23.000Z","msg":"多謝支持<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d24ba8a9a642d0924d816f2a6278c1cb07217465","tid":1024999,"uid":237361,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-20T15:45:38.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/3BD2iCP.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F3BD2iCP.png&h=feed64a5&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/nhKteba.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FnhKteba.png&h=6d859be0&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/iZy2iCR.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FiZy2iCR.png&h=2d763083&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n長艇停在一片水浸的森林前，我們兩人一對換乘小舢舨。柬國大媽撐著舢舨，帶領我們穿過樹林。<br />\n夕陽餘暉在枝葉間灑下，飄雲倒映在湖水上，很美。<br />\n她在船上看日落，看日落的我在旁邊看她。<br />\n夕陽裝飾了她的景象，她裝飾了我的夢。<br />\n其實她好像不太喜歡卞之琳。<br />\n沒關係，我喜歡。"},{"pid":"35f18979ae46b61c133af736442917805ab1bfbe","tid":1024999,"uid":237361,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-20T16:10:32.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"127eebc23dc201e39839a70e39cfdcc72740b041","tid":1024999,"uid":59649,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-21T14:11:46.000Z","msg":"留名"},{"pid":"2745e1ddbba7f802981c6f5f0aef29ae3b37f020","tid":1024999,"uid":237361,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-21T14:53:21.000Z","msg":"這幾天一覺醒來，發現床上都有點點血跡。<br />\n仔細看看，才知道自己昨夜輾轉反側，不自覺地壓死了幾隻不知名的小蟲。<br />\n之後，我在金邊的赤柬屠殺博物館，<br />\n走入由學校課室改建的囚室，望見牆上的受害者黑白照片、房中央的鐵床架、床兩端的手扣腳鐐、地上深深蝕入木板的血跡。<br />\n我忽爾想起在我床上死去的蟲子和那一點點嫣紅。"},{"pid":"52bbf3f12ba65662ca6e9c025ac8f02d90305a50","tid":1024999,"uid":237361,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-22T03:55:27.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/SEeAQF2.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FSEeAQF2.png&h=486a6ef4&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ZRtemNK.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FZRtemNK.png&h=f4b826e5&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/A3SnvF6.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FA3SnvF6.png&h=121ccbca&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/dVWrXk9.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FdVWrXk9.png&h=14e79d7a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n金邊是一個截然不同的城市。<br />\n作為首都，它是柬埔寨政治和經濟的中心。對遊客而言，它所背負的赤柬歷史血跡斑斑，實在值得了解。<br />\n尤其對我們香港人來說，那段慘絕人寰的赤柬統治似曾相識，近代的共產主義史大抵也是如此，聽起來像是弔詭的平行時空。<br />\n生於安穩，我們很難想像一個政治理念能夠如此徹底地摧毁一個社群的所有認知，包括宗教、傳統、文化、知識、社會規範、倫理關係，以至一切根深蒂固的價值。"},{"pid":"0ce23c56710f1abad1bc810fb9bcf42cf4091160","tid":1024999,"uid":237361,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-22T14:49:58.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/fJQcWxF.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FfJQcWxF.png&h=4a475e18&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n金邊最著名的一個地方叫殺戮戰場。<br />\n那裡曾經是赤柬政權的大屠殺場所，後來就成了無數受難者的亂葬崗。<br />\n現今整個地方的中央，座立一棟十七層高的白色佛塔，每一層都有玻璃箱，裏面放着滿滿的死難者頭骨，清晰可見有老有少死狀不一。<br />\n四周除了一兩間展覽室，其餘都是稻田和草地。往深處走去，更有一片清淨的湖。<br />\n寧靜之下，你卻總能感受到淡淡的戾氣，或者是因為一些小徑兩旁仍可見白骨在地，像是牙齒，又像是碎骨。"},{"pid":"e84b5384a7acefa869228886aa66329970c04f0d","tid":1024999,"uid":98659,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-22T15:08:39.000Z","msg":"樓主可以拎諾貝爾文學獎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1604f46ac4a9b401c5fc675b3f29756e4471eddd","tid":1024999,"uid":135995,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-22T15:26:52.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/V7HiSh8.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FV7HiSh8.png&h=73a6e816&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/bVXnzwu.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FbVXnzwu.png&h=4533aa9b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n大吳哥真係好靚 我六月去得兩三個人 不過好熱"},{"pid":"137fe527ee438fe62d2f69f2444c3720d92e5f06","tid":1024999,"uid":237361,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"1604f46ac4a9b401c5fc675b3f29756e4471eddd","tid":1024999,"uid":135995,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-22T15:26:52.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/V7HiSh8.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FV7HiSh8.png&h=73a6e816&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/bVXnzwu.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FbVXnzwu.png&h=4533aa9b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n大吳哥真係好靚 我六月去得兩三個人 不過好熱"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-22T15:50:50.000Z","msg":"竟然咁少人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a16fc2cd227edb9794820ea1221daed1110fdab2","tid":1024999,"uid":60668,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-22T16:24:31.000Z","msg":"鄺體 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a656ab0585617edb76c2a8b0023af7ef353b711c","tid":1024999,"uid":191921,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-22T16:25:33.000Z","msg":"文筆好撚差<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4915a7df53e28fcfe9678a74680054a3acc56cd0","tid":1024999,"uid":72244,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-22T16:35:52.000Z","msg":"欣賞樓主用書面語寫<br />\n但有陣時圖字不合<br />\n又會寫得太突兀，做多左<br />\n睇到好炆<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c0e75b080c4c317414ed390d6c84801da5adb17a","tid":1024999,"uid":237361,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"4915a7df53e28fcfe9678a74680054a3acc56cd0","tid":1024999,"uid":72244,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-22T16:35:52.000Z","msg":"欣賞樓主用書面語寫<br />\n但有陣時圖字不合<br />\n又會寫得太突兀，做多左<br />\n睇到好炆<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-22T16:47:02.000Z","msg":"多謝巴打你意見<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n本身其實一早諗好咗大概寫乜 不過冇圖好似冇乜人睇 所以先求其搵番幾張係嗰個地方嘅相"},{"pid":"cd1854af99d548b653c0d7045b0032643c2d113e","tid":1024999,"uid":237361,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-23T04:53:11.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/KnjM5Fj.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FKnjM5Fj.png&h=6f77f937&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n看過沉重的歷史，彼得提議到酒吧街輕鬆一下。<br />\n我們一行四人隨便選了間酒吧，喝了幾輪shot，點了兩支廉價的烈酒。<br />\n喝得興起，就到舞池隨意扭動，大家都想在假期的最後一晚狂歡盡興。<br />\n朱莉亞最先喝醉，人已經軟癱在梳化上，還一邊說著法文，<em>l'impossibilit&eacute; d'aimer dans notre temps</em>，一邊抄起酒瓶直接往喉嚨裡灌。"}]}